<div class="container">
  <% if flash.has?(:message) %>
    <h3 style="color:#F00"><%= flash[:message] %></h3>
  <% end %>
<% if session[:user_id] %>
  <h2>Welcome to Roam Scope <%=session[:username].capitalize%></h2>
<% else %>
  <h2>Welcome to Roam Scope</h2>
<% end %>
</br>
<h4>Arriving alone in a new city can be hard, unless you know a local who can easily tell you what you need to know.</h4>
<h4>Roam Scope is an attempt to make a system where the insights of locals can be captured and curated.</h4>
</br>
<% if session[:user_id] %>
<h2>To get started:</h2>
<ul>
